quran[21{c,v,t}:
51,31,"ibrahim ne kaha"" ae farstadgan Ellahi, kya muhim aap ko Dur paish hai ?"
51,32,"unhon ne kaha"" hum aik mujrim qoum ki taraf beje gay hain"
51,33,taakay uss par paki hui matti ke pathar barsa den
51,34,"jo aap ke rab ke haan hadd se guzar jaane walon ke liye nishaan zada hain """
51,35,phir hum ne unn sab logon ko nikaal liya jo uss bastii mein momin thay
51,36,aur wahan hum ne aik ghar ke siwa musalmanoon ka koi ghar nah paaya
51,37,is ke baad hum ne wahan bas aik nishani unn logon ke liye chore di jo dard naak azaab se drtay hon
51,38,aur ( tumahray liye nishani hai ) moose ke qissay mein jab hum ne ussay Sarih sanad ke sath firaon ke paas bheja
51,39,to woh apne bil botay par akarr gaya aur bola yeh jadugar hai ya majnu hai
51,40,aakhir-kaar hum ne ussay aur is ke lashkaron ko pakra aur sab ko samandar mein pheink diya aur woh malamat zada ho kar reh gaya
51,41,"aur ( tumahray liye nishani hai ) Aad mein, jabkay hum ne un par aik aisi be kher howa bhaij di"
51,42,ke jis cheez par bhi woh guzar gayi usay boseedah kar ke rakh diya
51,43,"aur ( tumahray liye nishani hai ) samood mein, jab unn se kaha gaya tha ke aik khaas waqt taq mazay kar lau"
51,44,magar is tanbeeh par bhi unhon ne apne rab ke hukum se sartabi ki aakhir-kaar un ke dekhte dekhte aik achanak toot parney walay azaab ne unn ko aa liya
51,45,phir nah unn mein uthnay ki sakt thi aur nah woh apna bachao kar satke thay
51,46,aur un sab se pehlay hum ne Nooh ki qoum ko halaak kya kyunkay woh fasik log thay
51,47,aasman ko hum ne apne zor se banaya hai aur hum iss ki qudrat rakhtay hain
51,48,zameen ko hum ne bichhaya hai aur hum barray achay hamwar karne walay hain
51,49,"aur har cheez ke hum ne jore banaye hain, shayad ke tum is se sabaq lau"
51,50,"Tu doDoroo Allah ki taraf, mein tumahray liye is ki taraf se saaf saaf khabardaar karne wala hon"
51,51,"aur nah banaao Allah ke sath koi dosra mabood, mein tumahray liye uss ki taraf se saaf saaf khabardaar karne wala hon"
